      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors and groups... i dont know. they all just say \"it gets better\" or \"give it time.\" but time is the problem. time is just more hours of this silence. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting a house that was meant for two people. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just... a complete lack of a reason to exist. how am i supposed to just keep going when half of me is literally gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
